item.title: Come Dice With Me 5 - Canapés Under Canvas
item.description: For the next few weeks we're playing Kieron Gillen's dinner party RPG Come Dice With Me! In the final episode will Velder prove to be a wizard in the kitchen? Or will his fortunes run out? You can pick up Come Dice with me for free by going here This episode originally aired on the DCP Patreon in 2020.
